{"tid":1144473,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《POKÉMON 神探Pikachu》首輪影評激讚：史上最佳遊戲改編電影","createTime":"2019-05-08T06:00:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T08:48:01.000Z","uid":152432,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"426a874f6cc60f1d3f2159969a28ca855b7dc487","tid":1144473,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T06:00:49.000Z","msg":"雖然現在全世界都陷入《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》（Avengers 4: Endgame）的漩渦裏，但還有一小批粉絲們，也很殷切期盼《POK&Eacute;MON 神探Pikachu》（Detective Pikachu）的到來，畢竟能夠看到萌度破表的小精靈們登上大銀幕，光是想到就覺得超級療癒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTQnTBi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTQnTBi.jpg&h=e824a1f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而近期《POK&Eacute;MON 神探Pikachu》在日本舉行首映，首波評價正式出爐，影評人們一致認同這部電影可愛度爆表！如果你對遊戲改編電影常常感到擔憂，現在你可以暫時放心了。<br />\n<br />\nComicBook網站的Megan Peters：「《POK&Eacute;MON 神探Pikachu》會引起轟動！不論你是精靈寶可夢的新舊粉絲，都會很喜歡這部作品。傳奇影業（Legendary Pictures, Inc.）成功打造一部很棒的改編電影。我整場都笑得很開心，而且感到很激動。而這部電影代表着開始。」<br />\nDEN OF GEEK網站編輯David Crow：「《POK&Eacute;MON 神探Pikachu》輕易地就成為有史以來最好的遊戲改編電影，對於看精靈寶可夢長大的人來說，這真的是一部很開心的電影。電影裏Ryan Reynolds的表現非常值得讚賞。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zVH189G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzVH189G.jpg&h=c1ec1fc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCollider網站編輯Dave Trumbore：「在日本看完《POK&Eacute;MON 神探Pikachu》的首映，我只希望「萊姆市」（Ryme City）是真的存在，我真的想要一個小精靈夥伴。」<br />\nIGN網站的Terri Schwartz：「故事非常療癒且有很棒的轉折，節奏也很流暢。Ryan Reynolds呈現出不同於死侍（Deadpool）的驚艷「聲音」演出，Justice Smith以及Kathryn Newton在電影裏也充滿魅力，戲裏的黑色幽默元素非常討喜。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2pTEbod.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2pTEbod.jpg&h=3ff9a8e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電影媒體The Nerds of Color：「《POK&Eacute;MON 神探Pikachu》真的很有趣。電影帶領我們深入小精靈世界，絕對讓鐵粉們意猶未盡。尤其電影裏滿滿的懷舊感，更易引起共鳴。這同時也是一部讓你又哭又笑的電影。Ryan Reynolds和Justice Smith的表現真的很棒！」<br />\nA.V. Club網站編輯Marah Eakin：「看完《POK&Eacute;MON 神探Pikachu》的第一個反應：超級可愛！全家人都可以從電影獲得樂趣，小精靈粉絲們理當很喜歡，但就算非鐵粉也能樂在其中，不自覺被深深吸引，最後：我超想抱抱比卡超。」"},{"pid":"1c787222c523a06133c1777cfe891d632c37d626","tid":1144473,"uid":152432,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T06:02:48.000Z","msg":"期待下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9PcBdB8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9PcBdB8.jpg&h=f61ce1c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kDYHTB9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkDYHTB9.jpg&h=fc2f26f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bmmVuav.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbmmVuav.jpg&h=66637cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qZ5GpJR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqZ5GpJR.jpg&h=c804027e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4556d776f1f34ea433eef073873ec14a690e64a6","tid":1144473,"uid":34869,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T06:13:45.000Z","msg":"還好個導演冇拉高隻比卡超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ffeb0b18156d70ce338f2c7c76392841668750","tid":1144473,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T06:14:32.000Z","msg":"期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a702120b46d92a4b12ac0858c2a8c460c617c24b","tid":1144473,"uid":26332,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T06:15:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>仆街任天堂，死都要改比卡丘，落地獄啦</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"16cbff8361913a1400f03d2f71c7cccc670934b2","tid":1144473,"uid":206594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T06:15:12.000Z","msg":"鬼佬無特登真實化啲精靈都幾值得一讚<br />\n只係加返啲text